data.description: Beautifully remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with an excellent view of Brentwood Park. When you walk through the door, you truly will be amazed! New interior features include recessed lighting throughout the 2474 sq ft home, new bathroom vanities, new kitchen cabinets, countertops, dishwasher and stove, new laminate flooring, and much more. Four large bedrooms allow flexibility for today's families. The spacious living room eliminates any worries about your wrap around couch fitting! The new black roof allows the exterior to be painted a beautiful white with front door pop of color. Remember, that a new roof will provide a lower insurance rate possible. Interested? Then, please call for a showing time today.
